T*
(- Fee floor: 250 atoms/vB \(2.5e-7 ATHO/vB\).) Tj
T*
(- Fee routing: pre-tail 40% to consensus pool, post-tail 50% to consensus pool.) Tj
T*
(- Tail burn target on non-pool share: 100% burn / 0% miner, with floor clipping.) Tj
T*
(- Supply floor: 21,000,000 ATHO.) Tj
T*
(- Protocol deflation threshold: ~44.64% sustained utilization.) Tj
