(- Net per-block formula: Delta_block = 0.1953125 - \(0.4375 * utilization\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Per year at full utilization) Tj
T*
(- Tail issuance: 0.1953125 * 262,800 = 51,328.125 ATHO/year) Tj
T*
(- Total annual fees at floor: 229,950 ATHO/year) Tj
T*
(- Annual burn-path max \(50%\): 114,975 ATHO/year) Tj
T*
(- Annual net formula: Delta_year = 51,328.125 - \(114,975 * utilization\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Deflation Threshold) Tj
T*
(Set annual net to zero:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(51,328.125 - 114,975u = 0) Tj
T*
(u = 51,328.125 / 114,975 ~= 0.4464) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(So:) Tj
T*
(- <44.64%: inflationary protocol net.) Tj
T*
(- =44.64%: neutral.) Tj
T*
(- >44.64%: deflationary protocol net \(until floor clipping binds\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
